Khashm El Girba Airport

Khashm El Girba Airport is a airport and is located in Sudan. The estimate terrain elevation above seal level is 481 metres. Variant forms of spelling for Khashm El Girba Airport or in other languages: HSKG (icao), GBU (iata). You can find more informations about Khashm El Girba Airport like tourist guide, accomodation on en.wikipedia.org
